{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_101","type":"agent_message","text":"The live run confirms the same blocker: `ReflectUtils` first probes the invalid array alias `\"[Lbyte;\"`, and native-image throws before cglib can fall back to the valid primitive descriptor. I’m checking whether this repository or Graal’s metadata loader has any supported way to encode that alias; if not, the remaining fix has to move into the test harness rather than the metadata file."}}
